title: ADVISORY Presidential Announcement at 10 15AM EDT | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




May 26, 2009

 



ADVISORY Presidential Announcement at 10 15AM EDT




THE WHITE HOUSE  Office of the Press Secretary      _____________________________________________ FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE          May 26, 2009   **MEDIA ADVISORY** President to Make Announcement at 10:15AM EDT Washington, D.C. – The President will make an announcement regarding his nomination for the Supreme Court at 10:15AM EDT in the East Room. The event will be open press.  Pre-set: 9:30AM EDT Final Gather: 9:45AM EDT Gather at the North Doors of the Palm Room ##
